Functions:
Menu: Display options and return user choice.
ADDPATIENTS:
Prompt for patient details, validate gender, write to patient.txt, increment count.
ADDDOCTORS:
Prompt for doctor details, write to doctorfile.txt, increment doc_count.
DISPLAYPATIENTS:
Read and print patient details from patient.txt.
DISPLAYDOCTORS:
Read and print doctor details from doctorfile.txt
